{"tid":1985162,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"著名生物學家道金斯 Richard Dawkins：冠狀病毒導致普通感冒","createTime":"2020-04-23T03:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T07:53:46.000Z","uid":149978,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8d331be8d51adb2d437e46435ff1ae3b7c10eabc","tid":1985162,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEqJpip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEqJpip.jpg&h=c660c194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/richarddawkins/status/1245475098787627008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fricharddawkins%2Fstatus%2F1245475098787627008&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6hR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=c6f4186d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/richarddawkins/status/1245475098787627008</a><br />\n<br />\n好明顯今次搞到外國咁大獲，係世衛改錯名<br />\n<br />\n最怕改壞名：冠狀病毒感覺上冇肺炎咁嚴重。2003年叫嚴重急性呼吸道綜合症，人人警揚，好快令沙士病毒消失。現在世衛將隻病叫2019年冠狀病毒病，完全無逼切嚴重性的感覺。早前台灣學者一早叫世衛改名做武漢急性呼吸道綜合症，Wuhan Acute Respiratory Syndrome (WARS)，WARS令人感覺像打杖一樣，警覺性大些，可惜世衛唔聽。護中國，反歧視，咪直接叫SARS Type B或者SARS II，即係乙型沙士或沙士第二代，又唔聽。叫咩冠狀病毒，連著名生物學家都被誤導。"},{"pid":"df2fe426e91a3c76b2e01d32b313969435458d42","tid":1985162,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T03:27:04.000Z","msg":"樓主ive仔？<br />\n<br />\n你唔明就縮返入老母西溫下書先啦<br />\n<br />\n弱智"},{"pid":"e6b002d7a0731c8f4da2693ee17061590fa36342","tid":1985162,"uid":338262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df2fe426e91a3c76b2e01d32b313969435458d42","tid":1985162,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T03:27:04.000Z","msg":"樓主ive仔？<br />\n<br />\n你唔明就縮返入老母西溫下書先啦<br />\n<br />\n弱智"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T03:29:28.000Z","msg":"五毛發現"},{"pid":"b8597222c5b34a310db4b63ff8b324fd03735dcb","tid":1985162,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e6b002d7a073